<span id="freeTextContainer5842798956897736881">Louise Erdrich’s <i>The Last Report on the Miracles at Little No Horse</i> should be recognized as an American classic: a wonderful and wonderfully told story, full of humanity, humor, mystery, and nuance. </span>

